OL,3,CNumber of serious burns from hot water
OL,4,Cbottles double in last five years
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has
OL,7,Funcovered confusion and
OL,8,Finconsistencies surrounding how long
OL,9,Fhot water bottles are safe to use, as
OL,10,FITV News' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThe number of serious burns caused by
OL,14,Fhot water bottles has almost doubled
OL,15,Fin the last five years, new data
OL,16,Fshared with ITV News shows.
OL,18,FIn 2024, 968 people in England and
OL,19,FWales were admitted to burn units
OL,20,Fcompared to 501 in 2020, according to
OL,21,Fthe International Burn Injury Database.
