OL,6,FWhile an NHS trust guidance states
OL,7,Fthat hot water bottles have a two-year
OL,8,Flifespan, ITV News found that some
OL,9,Fbeing sold by a variety of retailers
OL,10,Fwere already older than that.
OL,12,FResearchers found that the older hot
OL,13,Fwater bottles become, the more likely
OL,14,Fthey are to split.
OL,16,FDani Champion, 34, from Staffordshire,
OL,17,Fhas a vascular disorder and used to
OL,18,Fregularly seek comfort in her hot
OL,19,Fwater bottle to help cope with pain.
