OL,6,FIn January, Dani experienced pain that
OL,7,Fshe described as "more painful than
OL,8,Fchildbirth" when the hot bottle she
OL,9,Fwas using burst while she was sitting
OL,10,Fon the sofa.
OL,12,F"Shock set in quickly when it first
OL,13,Fhappened, I've never screamed like
OL,14,Fthat in my life. I ran to the shower
OL,15,Fto cool down and my skin just started
OL,16,Fbubbling up," she told ITV News.
