OL,6,F"As part of the recovery process at
OL,7,Fthe burns unit, every two days they
OL,8,Fwould use a really rough scouring like
OL,9,Fcloth and the back of a razor blade to
OL,10,Ftreat the wound.
OL,12,F"I was having nightmares about this
OL,13,Fhappening to my kids. If something
OL,14,Flike this happened to a child there is
OL,15,Fno coming back. Their skin wouldn't be
OL,16,Fable to heal like this."
OL,18,FDani had to stay at Birmingham Burns
OL,19,FUnit for a week, where she was
OL,20,Fadministered morphine and ketamine to
OL,21,Fmanage her pain.
