OL,6,FOnce discharged, she had regular check-
OL,7,Fups and used crutches for three weeks.
OL,9,FFortunately Dani is no longer in pain
OL,10,Fand is hoping that her story can be a
OL,11,Fwarning to others.
OL,13,F"There needs to be more talk about hot
OL,14,Fwater bottle safety," she added.
OL,16,FKen Dunn, a retired consultant burns
OL,17,Fand plastic surgeon who is now the
OL,18,Fvice chair of The Children's Burns
OL,19,FTrust (CBT), said they have seen an
OL,20,Fincreasing number of injuries because
OL,21,Fof hot water bottles.
