OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "We've identified an
OL,7,Fincreasing number of injuries,
OL,8,Fparticularly in children and the
OL,9,Felderly, over the last few years and
OL,10,Funfortunately this trend does not seem
OL,11,Fto be stopping.
OL,13,F"We're keen to get the message across
OL,14,Ffrom the CBT and other involved
OL,15,Fcharities that people can prevent
OL,16,Fthese injuries happening in their own
OL,17,Fhome and with their own family.
OL,19,F"These injuries tend to affect the
OL,20,Fhands, feet and shorts areas which are
OL,21,Fparticularly difficult to treat.
