OL,6,F"The major concern is damaged skin
OL,7,Fbecause it is an important organ that
OL,8,Fkeeps out infection, so when skin
OL,9,Fbecomes damaged it becomes a window
OL,10,Ffor infection."
OL,12,FResearchers from the University of
OL,13,FLiverpool found that the older a hot
OL,14,Fwater bottle gets, the more likely
OL,15,Fthey are to split.
OL,17,FDr Ahmed Abass, a lecturer in
OL,18,Fbiomedical engineering, said: "Rubber
OL,19,Fdegrades by time and by being subject
OL,20,Fto the atmosphere and oxygen. It also
OL,21,Fdegrades by heat and light."
