OL,6,FTheir research showed that the weak
OL,7,Fareas in the hot water bottles design
OL,8,Fare around the nicks and edges, and
OL,9,Fthe "highest stress concentration
OL,10,Fareas exist in the internal boundary
OL,11,Fof hot water bottles near the neck and
OL,12,Fcap region."
OL,14,F"The findings support the guidance
OL,15,Fthat users should avoid sleeping with
OL,16,Fa hot water bottle as it may fail
OL,17,Funder compression if they lay on top
OL,18,Fof it," the report said.
