OL,6,FLast year, the British Standards
OL,7,FInstitute (BSI) guidance on hot water
OL,8,Fbottles was withdrawn because the
OL,9,Fnational committee responsible for hot
OL,10,Fwater bottle safety was disbanded.
OL,12,FToday, retailers continue to sell hot
OL,13,Fwater bottles with reference to the
OL,14,Fhistoric guidance.
OL,16,FThe Royal Society for the Prevention
OL,17,Fof Accidents (ROSPA) and the CBT would
OL,18,Flike to see an updated BSI guideline
OL,19,Fpublished.
